co Lastrucci for The New York Times</media:credit><media:description> Sant&#39;Angelo 村及其凝灰岩小岛 La Torre 是伊斯基亚岛最美丽的村庄之一。</media:description></item><item><title>庆祝六月节，奴隶制结束的日子</title><link/>https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/09/travel/juneteenth-celebrations.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/09/travel/juneteenth-celebrations.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/09/travel/juneteenth-celebrations.html" rel="standout"></atom:link><description> 6 月 19 日，美国各地将以音乐、艺术、美食和烟花庆祝 6 月 19 日。我们重点介绍五个地方的项目，包括被称为假期发源地的德克萨斯州加尔维斯顿。</description><dc:creator>雪拉·马丁</dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 09 Jun 2023 09:00:53 +0000</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">六月十五日</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">加尔维斯顿（得克萨斯州）</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">洛杉矶（加利福尼亚州）</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">玛莎葡萄园岛（马萨诸塞州）</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">克利夫兰 (俄亥俄州)</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">汉普顿路 (弗吉尼亚州)</category></item><item><title>一个新网站帮助旅行者找到最便宜的酒店房间</title><link/>https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/08/travel/hotel-booking-websites.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/08/travel/hotel-booking-websites.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/08/travel/hotel-booking-websites.html" rel="standout"></atom:link><description>该网站提供酒店优惠，然后监控价格变化，是价格窃取旅游游戏中的最新参与者。</description><dc:creator>伊莱恩·格鲁萨克</dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 08 Jun 2023 16:55:51 +0000</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">旅行和假期</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">预算旅行</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">酒店和旅游住宿</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">HotelSlash公司</category><media:content height="151" medium="image" url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2023/06/12/business/11bizsky-hotelslash-print/02FrugalTraveler-illo-moth.jpg" width="151"></media:content><media:credit>克里斯蒂娜·朱</media:credit></item><item><title>这些轮椅正在帮助残疾旅客享受海滩</title><link/>https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/07/travel/beach-wheelchairs-disabled-travel.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/07/travel/beach-wheelchairs-disabled-travel.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/07/travel/beach-wheelchairs-disabled-travel.html" rel="standout"></atom:link><description>越来越多的美国海滩提供带有气球状轮胎的轮椅，为残疾人及其家人提供了更多享受阳光乐趣的选择。</description><dc:creator>卡伦天使</dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 07 Jun 2023 09:00:30 +0000</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">残疾</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">海滩</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">轮椅</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">旅行和假期</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">加州海岸委员会</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">MMGY全球</category><media:content height="151" medium="image" url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2023/06/01/multimedia/00beach-wheelchairs-tbpm/00beach-wheelchairs-tbpm-moth.jpg" width="151"></media:content><media:credit> Janel Kilnisan for The New York Times</media:credit><media:description>迈阿密的沙滩轮椅。这些椅子通常有超大、厚实的轮胎，可以让它们在沙地和不平坦的地形上滚动，有些型号甚至可以漂浮。</media:description></item><item><title> LGBTQ 旅行者冒险前往同性恋是非法的地方</title><link/>https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/06/travel/lgbtq-vactation-gay-rights.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/06/travel/lgbtq-vactation-gay-rights.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/06/travel/lgbtq-vactation-gay-rights.html" rel="standout"></atom:link><description>热带珊瑚礁、狩