multimedia/05travel-icebergs-gjbk/05travel-icebergs-gjbk-moth.jpg" width="151"></media:content><media:credit>托尼塞尼科拉/纽约时报</media:credit><media:description>纽芬兰特威林盖特镇附近的游船上的客人正在接近一座冰山。</media:description></item><item><title>与任何年龄最好的朋友一起环游世界</title><link/>https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/07/travel/travel-the-world.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/07/travel/travel-the-world.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/07/travel/travel-the-world.html" rel="standout"></atom:link><description>埃莉诺·汉比 (Eleanor Hamby) 和桑德拉·黑兹利普 (Sandra Hazelip) 博士在 81 岁高龄时用了 80 天时间从南极洲冰冷的海岸前往岩石雄伟的大峡谷。</description><dc:creator>詹妮弗·哈兰</dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 07 Jun 2023 09:01:28 +0000</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">旅行和假期</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">友谊</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">年龄，年代</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">内容类型：个人简介</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_per">埃莉诺·汉比 (1941- )</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_per">黑兹利普，桑德拉</category><media:content height="151" medium="image" url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2023/05/30/multimedia/00Never-Too-Late-Globetrotters-01-bgcl/00Never-Too-Late-Globetrotters-01-bgcl-moth.jpg" width="151"></media:content><media:credit>纽约时报的克里斯托弗·李</media:credit><media:description>Sandra Hazelip 博士（左）和 Eleanor Hamby 在环游世界时成为社交媒体的红人，获得了数百万粉丝的“赞”。</media:description></item><item><title>旧世界的 Horezu 陶器能否经得起现代品味的考验？</title><link/> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/03/style/horezu-pottery-ceramics-romania.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/03/style/horezu-pottery-ceramics-romania.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/03/style/horezu-pottery-ceramics-romania.html" rel="standout"></atom:link><description>罗马尼亚小镇制作了几个世纪的陶器风格最近成为热门商品。</description><dc:creator> Chantel Tattoli 和 Marko Risovic</dc:creator><pubDate> Sat, 03 Jun 2023 13:38:00 +0000</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">陶瓷和陶器</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">工艺品</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">霍雷祖（罗马尼亚）</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">罗马尼亚</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">联合国教育、科学及文化组织</category></item><item><title>阻止飞机坠毁的唐·贝特曼 (Don Bateman) 去世，享年 91 岁</title><link/>https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/02/technology/don-bateman-dead.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/02/technology/don-bateman-dead.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/02/technology/don-bateman-dead.html" rel="standout"></atom:link><description>他的驾驶舱警告系统可以在飞机飞向山峰、建筑物或海洋时向机组人员发出警报，从而挽救了数千人的生命。</description><dc:creator>理查德桑多米尔</dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 08 Jun 2023 13:25:20 +0000</pubDate><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_per">唐·贝特曼 (1932-2023)</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">死亡（讣告）</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">航空公司和飞机</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">航空事故、安全和灾难</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">传感器</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">工程和工程师</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org">霍尼韦尔国际公司</category></item><item><title>在一个不可思议的大国度进行伟大的、不可思议的旅程</title><link/>https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/02/world/australia/australia-journeys-uni-scooter.html<guid ispermalink="true"> https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/02/world/australia/australia-journeys-uni-scooter.html </guid><atom:link href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/06/02/world/